1
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:33,250
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,290 --> 00:00:36,250
[Episode 8: Now I Know Your Heart]

3
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:50,000
My Lady.

4
00:00:50,710 --> 00:00:53,040
Thank you for helping me regain my senses.

5
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:55,050
Here in Yin-Yang Crossing,

6
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:58,030
there aren't many people who would show me

7
00:00:58,590 --> 00:00:59,450
such kindness.

8
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,200
Once my mind cleared,

9
00:01:10,650 --> 00:01:12,050
I remembered something.

10
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:16,230
That day in prison,

11
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:18,360
an elder told me

12
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:20,230
that if

13
00:01:21,630 --> 00:01:23,789
I could obtain Magistrate Bai's heart,

14
00:01:23,789 --> 00:01:26,520
I would possess
the greatest beauty in the world.

15
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:29,160
But at the time, I was so exhausted

16
00:01:29,770 --> 00:01:30,900
that I couldn't tell

17
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:32,250
whether it was real

18
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:33,660
or just a dream.

19
00:01:37,539 --> 00:01:39,900
Do you remember what he looks like?

20
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:48,770
At first, he spoke with his back to me.

21
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:51,240
Then he slowly turned around.

22
00:02:02,110 --> 00:02:04,080
It's that one-eyed old man again!

23
00:02:07,050 --> 00:02:08,060
You should say,

24
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,740
it's Bai Han again.

25
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:11,310
Have you forgotten?

26
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:13,360
This is just Bai Han's vessel.

27
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:16,490
And he has more than just one vessel.

28
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,500
You're right.

29
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,490
There's also Bai Shanjun.

30
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,370
Anyway, I just want to know

31
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:26,460
how to retrieve the other half

32
00:02:26,460 --> 00:02:28,060
of the tree heart inside him.

33
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:30,610
Bai Han's cultivation is strong,

34
00:02:30,610 --> 00:02:32,010
and he's far too cunning.

35
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:34,100
Without the tree heart,

36
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:36,270
how can we possibly stand against him?

37
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,050
Born of evil power,

38
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,680
and nourished by it.

39
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:44,260
As long as evil power surges
in Yin-Yang Crossing,

40
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:47,710
he can continue absorbing it
to heal himself

41
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,290
and grow even stronger.

42
00:02:51,050 --> 00:02:51,860
Don't worry.

43
00:02:52,770 --> 00:02:55,300
It's fine if we can't
retrieve the tree heart.

44
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:58,020
We'll simply use
the county magistrate as bait.

45
00:02:58,930 --> 00:03:00,130
We can't keep letting

46
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,840
Bai Han lead us around by the nose.

47
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:17,190
[Dedication Above Self]

48
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:17,030
Greetings, My Lord!

49
00:03:17,770 --> 00:03:19,210
What are you doing?

50
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:23,650
Lord Bai, we treated you poorly
at Huichun Brothel the other day.

51
00:03:23,860 --> 00:03:25,530
I've felt guilty ever since.

52
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:28,880
I came here today specifically
to offer my apology.

53
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:29,390
Well...

54
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:31,210
Lord Bai is wise and upright,

55
00:03:31,230 --> 00:03:32,430
clean as still water,

56
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,900
and impartial as a mirror.

57
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,480
My deepest gratitude to you, Lord Bai.

58
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:35,930
Please, get up.

59
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:36,790
Thank you both.

60
00:03:37,020 --> 00:03:38,550
Guys, bring these stuff in.

61
00:03:38,610 --> 00:03:39,140
Yes, sir!

62
00:03:40,579 --> 00:03:41,110
Lord Bai.

63
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:42,340
Not bad.

64
00:03:44,370 --> 00:03:44,970
Thank you.

65
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,390
You're welcome.

66
00:03:47,090 --> 00:03:47,740
My Lord.

67
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,530
Our Yin-Yang Crossing

68
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:51,790
hasn't had a useful magistrate in years.

69
00:03:52,050 --> 00:03:52,770
Back then,

70
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,100
Xiqianhua took care of us,

71
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:55,620
so we didn't feel much difference.

72
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:57,810
But ever since you arrived,
things have become even better.

73
00:03:57,810 --> 00:03:58,579
Now,

74
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:01,210
many families don't even bother
locking their doors when they go out.

75
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:02,420
If someone finds money on the road,

76
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:04,210
they'll bring it straight
to the magistrate's office.

77
00:04:04,210 --> 00:04:05,740
All of this is thanks to you.

78
00:04:06,090 --> 00:04:06,930
Besides,

79
00:04:07,370 --> 00:04:08,580
Lady Fufeng's standards

80
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,220
have always been incredibly high.

81
00:04:10,220 --> 00:04:11,680
Since she approves of you,

82
00:04:11,770 --> 00:04:12,530
we naturally

83
00:04:12,530 --> 00:04:14,860
trust you as well.

84
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:17,529
Lady Fufeng approves of me?

85
00:04:17,899 --> 00:04:19,140
Of course.

86
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:20,899
I've never seen her

87
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:22,830
pay this much attention to anyone.

88
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,960
To be honest, this yamen

89
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:32,940
hasn't been this lively in years.

90
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,960
Back then,

91
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:38,350
if Lady Fufeng hadn't guarded this place,

92
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:41,080
it would have fallen into chaos long ago.

93
00:04:47,850 --> 00:04:51,450
When the sky fell, she was the one
at the front lines holding it up.

94
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:54,690
When order collapsed,
she rebuilt it with her own hands.

95
00:04:55,250 --> 00:04:58,020
The peace Yin-Yang Crossing enjoys today,

96
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:01,210
where humans and demons

97
00:05:01,210 --> 00:05:03,170
can live and make a living together,

98
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:04,880
exists all because of her.

99
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:09,570
She's the anchor of our Yin-Yang Crossing.

100
00:05:10,930 --> 00:05:13,490
And now that she stands behind you,

101
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,330
we trust her,

102
00:05:15,670 --> 00:05:17,400
so naturally, we trust you too.

103
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:39,630
Place your bets!

104
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:40,900
Small.

105
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,770
Big.

106
00:05:42,330 --> 00:05:43,290
I won again!

107
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:48,870
Magic and sorcery are strictly forbidden
at the Golden Toad Gambling House.

108
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:49,530
Move aside!

109
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:52,080
They're yours.

110
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,330
Thanks.

111
00:06:04,470 --> 00:06:05,590
What are you doing?

112
00:06:05,850 --> 00:06:06,650
Grandpa,

113
00:06:06,850 --> 00:06:09,140
why can't I ever
finish plucking your beard?

114
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:10,090
Is that so?

115
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:24,660
Magistrate Bai.

116
00:06:25,530 --> 00:06:26,620
Magistrate Bai.

117
00:06:28,970 --> 00:06:30,430
Do you want to play a round?

118
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:33,500
No, you guys go ahead.

119
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:35,650
Come on.

120
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,870
Big or small,

121
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:37,980
place your bets!

122
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:48,340
[The Magistrate's Office]

123
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:01,440
Master.

124
00:07:02,170 --> 00:07:03,940
Lately, petitions about theft

125
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:04,820
and neighborhood disputes

126
00:07:04,820 --> 00:07:06,350
have decreased significantly.

127
00:07:06,350 --> 00:07:08,710
They're probably being reported
to the county yamen now.

128
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:09,970
Looking at it this way,

129
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:12,090
that bookworm county magistrate

130
00:07:12,090 --> 00:07:13,290
is quite capable.

131
00:07:14,770 --> 00:07:15,960
How many of today's petitions

132
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,720
are related to evil power?

133
00:07:19,580 --> 00:07:22,650
Cases about panic, madness,
and beast attacks

134
00:07:22,890 --> 00:07:24,940
have increased 30 percent
compared to last month.

135
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:26,600
The dead field in West Village

136
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:28,420
is expanding again.

137
00:07:28,850 --> 00:07:31,110
If you've seen enough, just come inside.

138
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:42,020
My Lady.

139
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,300
Take a look if you want to.

140
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:51,170
It's fine.

141
00:07:54,690 --> 00:07:55,490
My Lady.

142
00:07:55,790 --> 00:07:57,980
Do you need to review these every day?

143
00:07:59,170 --> 00:08:00,230
Of course she does!

144
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:02,940
What kind of place
did you think the Xiqianhua Mansion was?

145
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:05,200
A gathering den for demons and monsters?

146
00:08:06,330 --> 00:08:07,060
Lord Bai,

147
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:08,990
it's not even 9 PM yet.

148
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:11,820
Why are you here so early?

149
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,900
My Lady, can we speak in private?

150
00:08:19,450 --> 00:08:19,910
My Lady.

151
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:23,400
Today, Madam Chun and Wan
came to the county yamen.

152
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:24,900
They talked a lot,

153
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:26,900
and I heard

154
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:28,910
many rumors about you.

155
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:33,299
Don't take Madam Chun's words
too seriously.

156
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,049
A thousand years is a long time.

157
00:08:36,789 --> 00:08:38,590
Even I can't remember most of it.

158
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:41,590
But the people have the clearest memory.

159
00:08:42,690 --> 00:08:43,900
It's far more real

160
00:08:44,290 --> 00:08:45,820
than any official records.

161
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,990
Lord Bai, did you hurry all the way here

162
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,210
just to tell me this?

163
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:53,280
Of course not.

164
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:54,560
My Lady,

165
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:57,610
I want to know the real Yin-Yang Crossing.

166
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:08,620
Can this willow tree

167
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,470
really connect to

168
00:09:11,490 --> 00:09:13,420
Yin-Yang Crossing's earth veins?

169
00:09:18,290 --> 00:09:18,890
Of course.

170
00:09:19,810 --> 00:09:20,270
My Lady,

171
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,420
what kind of demon are you?

172
00:09:25,830 --> 00:09:26,560
A tree demon.

173
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:28,390
A willow tree

174
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:31,160
that spent 1,000 years
cultivating a human form.

175
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:32,110
A willow tree?

176
00:09:39,670 --> 00:09:40,760
This spirit willow

177
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,510
is my true form.

178
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:48,200
I didn't know that.

179
00:09:52,170 --> 00:09:54,370
A willow tree can turn into a human form?

180
00:09:56,410 --> 00:09:58,410
No wonder the spiritual pool

181
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:00,410
uses these willow leaves to channel water.

182
00:10:00,410 --> 00:10:02,380
It feels like an endless supply.

183
00:10:02,810 --> 00:10:04,290
This willow tree is so big.

184
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:14,260
Lord Bai, you've improved a lot.

185
00:10:14,610 --> 00:10:16,210
Associating the willow tree

186
00:10:16,220 --> 00:10:17,530
with a spiritual pool,

187
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:22,340
you're starting to look more like
a true citizen of Yin-Yang Crossing.

188
00:10:22,900 --> 00:10:23,450
My Lady,

189
00:10:25,450 --> 00:10:27,180
when you spoke of willingness,

190
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,970
you wanted me to stay
in Yin-Yang Crossing of my own will,

191
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:31,680
didn't you?

192
00:10:35,170 --> 00:10:36,900
I was born into a humble family.

193
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,980
My original intention as an official

194
00:10:39,010 --> 00:10:40,470
was simply to help people.

195
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:43,560
So I devoted myself to my duties,

196
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:45,980
only to end up

197
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:47,450
taking the blame and being demoted

198
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:49,380
for a superior born into nobility.

199
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:51,740
When I first arrived at Yin-Yang Crossing,

200
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:53,740
I just let things take their course.

201
00:10:53,990 --> 00:10:55,080
But once I got here,

202
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,870
everything I've seen

203
00:10:57,210 --> 00:10:59,670
has overturned everything I once believed.

204
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:00,860
Lord Bai.

205
00:11:02,170 --> 00:11:03,700
Cut the bureaucratic tone.

206
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:06,400
My Lady, this is not a bureaucratic tone.

207
00:11:07,310 --> 00:11:08,820
After arriving at Yin-Yang Crossing,

208
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:10,720
for the first time, I truly feel that

209
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,430
I'm doing something as an official.

210
00:11:12,430 --> 00:11:15,070
And all of this was
because of you, My Lady.

211
00:11:18,380 --> 00:11:19,140
It seems

212
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:22,830
you've finally thought it through,
unyielding Lord Bai.

213
00:11:24,530 --> 00:11:25,290
But,

214
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:27,620
I cannot blindly

215
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:29,500
step into this world.

216
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:30,790
My Lady.

217
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:33,740
Please show me the real Yin-Yang Crossing.

218
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:35,690
Show me what it is you're protecting,

219
00:11:35,690 --> 00:11:36,620
and why...

220
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,480
it has to be me.

221
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:41,020
Once I see it clearly

222
00:11:41,050 --> 00:11:42,050
and figure it out,

223
00:11:42,770 --> 00:11:43,380
I will

224
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:46,290
stay here of my own free will.

225
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,220
Come see me tomorrow
between 7 AM and 9 AM.

226
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:56,220
Don't be late.

227
00:12:14,730 --> 00:12:17,010
This is the source of evil power?

228
00:12:17,810 --> 00:12:18,870
You could say that.

229
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,540
Only this lies at its very bottom.

230
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,250
It's the filth of this world

231
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:26,780
that cannot be dissolved or dispersed.

232
00:12:27,810 --> 00:12:30,650
It breeds greed, malice,

233
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,560
and the urge for self-destruction.

234
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:36,140
Why does something like this exist?

235
00:12:36,770 --> 00:12:38,030
Where did it come from?

236
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:42,320
Legend has it that Yin-Yang Crossing

237
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:45,450
was formed from the eye of the earth
when Pangu split heaven and earth apart.

238
00:12:45,450 --> 00:12:46,420
Above ground,

239
00:12:46,450 --> 00:12:47,750
spiritual power gathers

240
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:49,290
to nourish all living things.

241
00:12:49,290 --> 00:12:50,290
Below the ground,

242
00:12:50,530 --> 00:12:51,650
evil power surges endlessly,

243
00:12:51,650 --> 00:12:53,650
capable of destroying everything.

244
00:12:53,690 --> 00:12:54,400
That is why

245
00:12:55,050 --> 00:12:56,840
the land of Yin-Yang Crossing is fertile,

246
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,320
and all beings gain sentience

247
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,780
through spiritual power.

248
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:03,160
But it can also be devoured
by evil power at any moment.

249
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:04,540
This is the price.

250
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,090
A hundred years ago,

251
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:10,220
someone and I

252
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:16,020
barely managed to seal it.

253
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,710
If it's sealed,

254
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:21,250
why does it keep leaking out?

255
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:22,950
Look over there.

256
00:13:24,540 --> 00:13:26,660
A seal is like blocking a spring,

257
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:29,560
while evil power
is like underground water.

258
00:13:30,050 --> 00:13:32,050
It will always find another way out.

259
00:13:32,610 --> 00:13:34,650
We call these seepages.

260
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:36,970
There is no pattern

261
00:13:37,570 --> 00:13:39,350
to when or where they'll appear.

262
00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:41,430
What the Xiqianhua has been doing

263
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:44,560
for the last century
was simply mending the land,

264
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:47,360
suppressing evil power,
and purifying the earth.

265
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,970
With your spiritual power?

266
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:53,030
Spiritual power can drain,

267
00:13:53,450 --> 00:13:55,110
but the seepages never cease.

268
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:58,640
I don't know how much longer
we can keep mending it.

269
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,520
But recently,

270
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:04,480
these seepages have begun appearing
with alarming regularity.

271
00:14:05,450 --> 00:14:06,930
Are you saying

272
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:10,560
someone's deliberately
releasing evil power?

273
00:14:15,650 --> 00:14:16,450
What's wrong?

274
00:14:17,030 --> 00:14:19,030
Someone touched the seal. Get back!

275
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:40,610
Lady Fufeng.

276
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:42,900
Are you okay?

277
00:15:00,450 --> 00:15:01,300
What's this?

278
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:05,760
Suppressing the corruption
with my spiritual power.

279
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:16,930
Lady Fufeng.

280
00:15:41,690 --> 00:15:44,390
The corruption has invaded
her vital meridians.

281
00:15:44,390 --> 00:15:45,280
This time,

282
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:48,500
I'm afraid she won't be able
to hold on much longer.

283
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:49,670
What do you mean

284
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:52,300
she won't be able to hold on much longer?

285
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:53,980
Young Magistrate.

286
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:55,840
My Lady.

287
00:15:57,770 --> 00:15:59,170
If I truly pass away,

288
00:16:00,530 --> 00:16:01,560
can you govern

289
00:16:03,850 --> 00:16:05,310
Yin-Yang Crossing for me?

290
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:07,140
My Lady, you're a thousand-year-old demon.

291
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:08,300
I'm just a...

292
00:16:10,950 --> 00:16:11,740
My Lady?

293
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:16,020
Fengling.

294
00:16:16,230 --> 00:16:17,030
Come quickly.

295
00:16:18,950 --> 00:16:20,150
Check on Lady Fufeng.

296
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:21,650
What's happening to her?

297
00:16:29,210 --> 00:16:30,340
A hundred years ago,

298
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:33,030
Master gave half of her heart

299
00:16:33,290 --> 00:16:35,170
to her deputy at the time so they could

300
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:36,900
suppress evil power together.

301
00:16:40,220 --> 00:16:41,340
Unexpectedly,

302
00:16:42,170 --> 00:16:44,500
that jerk broke his word and betrayed her.

303
00:16:45,290 --> 00:16:47,620
The moment he got Master's power, he fled.

304
00:16:48,620 --> 00:16:49,570
Half a heart?

305
00:16:51,090 --> 00:16:52,020
Over the years,

306
00:16:53,140 --> 00:16:56,530
Master has been pushing through
with only half a heart.

307
00:16:57,860 --> 00:17:00,520
While maintaining order
of Yin-Yang Crossing,

308
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:03,410
she had to suppress
the corruption everywhere.

309
00:17:04,490 --> 00:17:07,020
Her spiritual power
has long been exhausted.

310
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:09,390
And she has reached her limit.

311
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:12,240
Then... how do we save her?

312
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:13,619
Do you know

313
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:17,500
why Master wanted you to stay?

314
00:17:18,490 --> 00:17:19,290
Why?

315
00:17:20,579 --> 00:17:22,510
Because whenever you're near her,

316
00:17:23,380 --> 00:17:26,060
her spiritual power recovers more quickly.

317
00:17:35,910 --> 00:17:37,330
Although you are a mortal,

318
00:17:37,330 --> 00:17:38,470
your physique is unique.

319
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:40,450
You are highly compatible with Master.

320
00:17:40,450 --> 00:17:43,380
And you can help Master
restore her spiritual power.

321
00:17:44,170 --> 00:17:44,970
So that's why

322
00:17:45,930 --> 00:17:47,380
you asked me to stay—

323
00:17:48,490 --> 00:17:50,220
only for your spiritual power.

324
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:53,350
I thought...

325
00:18:56,170 --> 00:18:56,650
My Lady.

326
00:19:01,930 --> 00:19:02,730
Didn't you say

327
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:06,440
your spiritual power
recovers faster when I'm around?

328
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:08,210
Just keep holding my hand.

329
00:19:11,970 --> 00:19:13,830
That won't be necessary anymore.

330
00:19:26,970 --> 00:19:29,620
All the records gathered
by Xiqianhua over the years

331
00:19:29,620 --> 00:19:31,880
are stored in the secret chamber behind.

332
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:34,430
You''ll find methods
of suppressing corruption,

333
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:36,160
records of land purification,

334
00:19:36,730 --> 00:19:37,970
civil cases,

335
00:19:39,170 --> 00:19:41,580
the traits of all kinds of demons,

336
00:19:42,010 --> 00:19:43,740
as well as how to regulate them.

337
00:19:54,410 --> 00:19:55,730
Didn't you want to know

338
00:19:56,470 --> 00:20:00,130
how to govern Yin-Yang Crossing
where humans and demons coexist?

339
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:03,050
Everything I can teach you

340
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:03,980
is in there.

341
00:20:11,970 --> 00:20:13,570
Go back to your county yamen.

342
00:20:14,340 --> 00:20:15,140
From now on,

343
00:20:16,490 --> 00:20:18,260
unless it's official business,

344
00:20:18,260 --> 00:20:20,260
there's no need to come see me again.

345
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:21,650
My Lady.

346
00:20:22,390 --> 00:20:23,280
What are you...

347
00:20:25,540 --> 00:20:26,490
Bai Shanjun,

348
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:28,920
you are free now.

349
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:32,820
My Lady.

350
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:35,540
I promise you.

351
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:37,990
I will stay.

352
00:20:58,560 --> 00:20:59,920
Well done.

353
00:21:02,860 --> 00:21:04,520
I can't extract a human heart.

354
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:07,040
This is the best I can do to help you.

355
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:09,140
Liu Fufeng's days are numbered.

356
00:21:09,770 --> 00:21:11,730
You can do whatever you want.

357
00:21:12,530 --> 00:21:14,130
Just don't look for me again.

358
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:18,100
You can't extract a human heart?

359
00:21:19,530 --> 00:21:21,150
If you hadn't run away just now,

360
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:22,450
wouldn't you have already succeeded?

361
00:21:22,450 --> 00:21:24,350
I wasn't thinking straight at the moment!

362
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:25,870
Since you are unwilling to take the heart,

363
00:21:25,870 --> 00:21:28,180
then give me all your spiritual power!

364
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:46,390
Fufeng,

365
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:48,790
we'll soon meet again.

